detailsSection: This white paper contains procedures to install and configure version control for Microsoft Dynamics AX 2009 using Microsoft Visual Studio Team Foundation Server. This paper is designed to be used in conjunction with the Team Server (ID Server) Setup white paper for Microsoft Dynamics AX 2009 and the Team Foundation Installation Guide for Visual Studio Team System.
